metadata.name: Thousands Year Later in the Dreamy Dunes
metadata.description:
1/1 minted by Hulki Okan Tabak, Where is Somewhere? smart contract, 2023

from the Somewhere project about Nowhere with characters Sometimes

mints on its own Manifold deployed smart contract and MakersPlace at this moment with new ones upcoming

planning a series of small Foundation drops about different chapters in the project

...

SOMEWHERE

Somewhere I was lost  
Seeking nothing  
Knowing no way  
Back Home  
I lost Somewhere some time ago

Wandering nonexistent landmarks  
Moonlight over drifting slopes  
Of sand  
Solitary appearances  
Sometimes a couple  
Mirage in a timeless zone  
Sometimes in Somewhere Not At All

by Hulki Okan Tabak, 2023
